description:
With over 200,000 images, and more every day, Fantastic Wallpaper Pro is the most full-featured, versatile and functional app for wallpaper. From Pop Culture to foreign cultures, it gives users the world in pictures. Each high resolution image has been perfectly formatted to fit the Palm Pre Touch screen and comes with a host of user-friendly features. Features: 

¶ 40+ Categories, 200,000+ Wallpapers…and counting 
¶ Beautiful Full Screen 
¶ Set as Wallpaper 
¶ Save into Photos 
¶ Search to get what you want 
¶ Fast Loading. 
¶ Stunning UI 
¶ Easy Navigation – Swipe, Zoom, Pinch 
¶ In-App Feedback for User Questions 
¶ New Wallpapers Added Daily 

Fantastic Wallpaper Free gives users thousands of ways to make their Palm Pre their own.
